item.title: Impossible Humans : The Vittorio Veneto Film Festival Shooting
item.description:
Impossible Humans : The Vittorio Veneto Film Festival Shooting

"Labels are for cans, not people" (Andy Warhol)During the seventh edition of Vittorio Film Festival (VVFF) and for the world's celebrations of #PolaroidWeek the New Era Museum is proud to present together with OperaArea Impossible Humans : The Vittorio Veneto Film Festival Shooting to be held April 22 to 24 at the photo-set of the Teatro da Ponte in Vittorio Veneto.
